    <h2>8. Recent Developments & Growth Catalysts</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      Analysis of recent business events and potential growth drivers.
    </p>

    <h3>Recent Business Developments:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>AXON 2.0 Rollout (Q1 2024):</strong> Enhanced machine learning capabilities result in improved performance metrics.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Geographic & Vertical Expansion:</strong> Increased penetration into non-gaming verticals and emerging markets.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Strategic Partnerships:</strong> Broader collaborations with major publishers and ad networks.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Executive Additions:</strong> Strengthened leadership with experienced hires in tech and finance.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Share Repurchase Activity:</strong> Significant buyback reducing outstanding shares and supporting EPS growth.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Growth Catalysts:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Continuous AI Enhancement:</strong> Ongoing development of the AXON platform driving advertising ROI.
      </li>
      <li>
